<promed@promedmail.org>
[For a map of Kazakhstan please see
<http://us.i1.yimg.com/us.yimg.com/i/travel/dg/maps/63/750x750_kazakhstan_m.gif>
This article does not provide us much information regarding the type of
mushroom or even the clinical signs. - Mod.TG
